N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 111.11 - Seed house or bin inspection of seed

State Regulations

One or more inspections of harvested lots of seeds to be
certified may be made at any time by authorized persons. Any lot not properly
stored, not properly protected from mixture, or not properly identified may be
rejected for certification. Notes
